{"tid":1117564,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[字海] 不要向神明胡亂祈禱......","createTime":"2019-04-20T18:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T06:53:27.000Z","uid":28823,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f2fe12ad57ebfdf71c2216aa4ed9d00bffd9b7","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"首先，我係好認真非假膠，我唔會無聊到凌晨2點係到派膠唔去訓教咁幼稚<br />\n兩年前，我為一件事向神明祈禱，是非常認真誠懇既祈禱，那個畫面我到現在還很記得....<br />\n我好想要一樣野，&quot;要&quot;之前係要去&quot;理解&quot;果樣野，而我現在經歷緊&quot;理解&quot;<br />\n直到現在，我才發現有些事情是開始了就沒有退路，事情只會不斷向前....<br />\n起初仲未發覺靈驗，但依家發覺越黎越靈，靈到我打從骨子裹害怕...<br />\n<br />\n我想退出，我再一次向神明祈禱，拒絕返兩年前既願望，結果無效....<br />\n神明唔會直接去達成你既&quot;願望&quot;，而係會安排好多野去令你&quot;經歷&quot;，最終&quot;達成&quot;<br />\n舉例 : 你向神明祈求考試一百分，前題你都要努力溫書同考試前唔打J....<br />\n<br />\n依兩年我不斷捲入好多事件入面，慢慢咁發現我成個人開始改變左...<br />\n無論思想,性格,心態,行為全部都變哂，我慢慢&quot;理解&quot;到我想要既&quot;果樣野&quot;...<br />\n經歷相同既感受先會有相同既想法，你想完全得到一樣野之前係要&quot;理解&quot;果樣野先..<br />\n<br />\n我，發覺唔對路了，因為好影響到我日常生活了，再係咁落去我會捱唔住，會崩潰...<br />\n點解我發覺唔對路? 係因為身邊有太多人都發覺我唔對路了而作出提醒了....<br />\n我好辛苦，好似走進迷宮入面，不斷輪迴不斷去摸索...我受夠了...好撚心寒...<br />\n我開始想返去兩年前，但已經回不去了，就好似高潮咁，射果下係停唔到，係返唔到轉頭...<br />\n同雪音一樣，唔過份追求就唔會出事，只係雪音咁好彩可以比神器用&quot;禊&quot;，救返出黎，我呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHpxpMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHpxpMh.jpg&h=7ae1f75d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，我覺得你地一定覺得我係到發神經9up，算啦，我都知我份人癲無乜人理解到...<br />\n但希望各位手足，祈禱/有人拜託人之前，真係要三思，有D野係要付出代價，等價交換...<br />\n<br />\n野良神第80話已經出左，大家快D睇唔該，以下兩張圖同我篇文係有關係，大家可以推算下..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czpA6Vz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczpA6Vz.jpg&h=4f100488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kop12tV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkop12tV.jpg&h=207620c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好邪，昆沙門既神器刺傷滅門loop左好多次，惠比壽既換代也loop左好多次....<br />\n夜卜殺人既命運都一直發生loop住落去，佢依家做福神要付出沉重代價.....<br />\n就係因為夜卜&quot;想要&quot;一樣野，所以佢要去&quot;理解&quot;一樣野，過程係好痛苦，但佢停唔到...<br />\n其實成件事都係悲劇，神明換代，神器祝器野良，神明最隱晦之事，天即是正。<br />\n<br />\n野良神真係好好睇，好有討論空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9677feb60ac4e4e209c9b76d7c68a509ef8a68c","tid":1117564,"uid":194785,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"Too long <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f252099a7098628643e902a53a190d2f67c2a","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"想認真論討論都咁難"},{"pid":"7d4116574dc7accb8335e75eeb4c3e1c00c6b5b7","tid":1117564,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"打左咁大篇野推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會睇下。"},{"pid":"736ef76e0672632f34a064a5f24bfc78101d0c97","tid":1117564,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"樓主牛b"},{"pid":"a4943b0d80747e00212eed695b9d31f62997733e","tid":1117564,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇了"},{"pid":"f6e9d599ec1f6d0330bc866874efffc1090fa331","tid":1117564,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"你向神祈禱都係神所期望的"},{"pid":"076c6111cda52c651bf9d96050750de48521da6d","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d4116574dc7accb8335e75eeb4c3e1c00c6b5b7","tid":1117564,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"打左咁大篇野推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會睇下。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"睇哂動畫兩季轉睇埋漫畫啦，無介紹錯嫁"},{"pid":"a1b88bfb9bb0504d63dd7699343aaa27b195ef5d","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6e9d599ec1f6d0330bc866874efffc1090fa331","tid":1117564,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"你向神祈禱都係神所期望的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"依樣真，神就係想我地祈禱，你好似領悟左某D野"},{"pid":"b0cd0c7b5b30c4ca7520431b3fbc88d388084fbf","tid":1117564,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"又係真物呀?"},{"pid":"ae836c37fa7a4c527d5d0568de7c5ef57e8021b4","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0cd0c7b5b30c4ca7520431b3fbc88d388084fbf","tid":1117564,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"又係真物呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"上次係講大老師，今次係講野良神"},{"pid":"2ecfd9afbd53cf61af104daeaa8763fa3ef57f61","tid":1117564,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"樓主一定係傳說中隱世於動物台嘅八奇高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda93966519af24211488d69787564dfb20b73f5","tid":1117564,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pSjhN51.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpSjhN51.gif&h=e783cf13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2f05c05abdc65f1729e19448989c91d945634a8","tid":1117564,"uid":151969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6f252099a7098628643e902a53a190d2f67c2a","tid":1117564,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"想認真論討論都咁難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"想認真討論去其他壇啦 唔好浪費時間係身兒登仔身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}